    "The control of the SLRIP system is based on two processes: the swing-up of and stabilization of the pendulum.",
    "The agents are developed to compute the swing angle of the pendulum until it achieves the upright position.",
    "When the pendulum is near the upright position (180° ± 10°) the proximal policy agent switches the stability action.",
    "A deep NN agent was implemented for the control of the DQNL.",
    "The parameters of the DQNL agent are presented in Table 4."
